org.apache.oodt.commons.object.jndi

Class HTTPContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.oodt.commons.object.jndi.HTTPContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Context

    public class HTTPContext
extends Object
implements Context
    This is a pseudo context that yields any name passed in as a URL, if it can be parsed as an URL.

    $Revision: 1.2 $
